Create Virtual Enviornment
python3 -m venv .venv

run this command in terminal to download dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt


create .env file which has the following

GROQ_API_KEY=<API KEY>
LANGSMITH_TRACING=true
LANGSMITH_ENDPOINT=https://api.smith.langchain.com
LANGSMITH_API_KEY=<KEY>
LANGSMITH_PROJECT="PROJECT NAME"

Run CLI pipeline:
python main.py

Run Phase-1 dashboard:
streamlit run app.py

Optional real map telemetry source (used by default path `data/driver_locations.csv`):
Required columns: driver_id + lat/lon (or latitude/longitude) + optional timestamp.

In Streamlit, open **Sidebar → Map Controls → Map mode → World (global view)** to see a world map.